# Test Rules

- New behavior needs automated tests.
- Mock external processes, ADB, Ollama, IDE CLIs, and network calls in unit tests.
- Keep tests focused on public functions, command routing, and user-visible behavior.
- Run default validation before reporting completion:

```bash
ruff check .
pytest
pro-ai-server validate-release
```

